texts.text: Isn't this venue on the small side?
C'mon, Shiori. It's more than enough for a star of your caliber.
Excuse me?
*Gulp* Glare all you want, but I'm not a miracle worker—
...! Breaktime. Go buy me lunch. Indian curry.
R-Right now? I don't even know if there's Indian curry around h—
Hup to it!!
Eep...
Phew, he's finally gone. Well then...
What rotten luck.
You could've gone to any club but just had to pick this one.
Okay, next is...
Yaaaay!
She looks like any normal little girl.
I agree. She's usually only around adults like us,
so it's important for her to play with other children sometimes.
I'll throw the frisbee next!
No! It's MY turn!!
Stop it! We're all friends, so let's play nice and take turns.
*Sniff* I'm sorry, Honey.
Yeah, sorry.
Good! That's much better!
Haha! They look up to her as a big sister.
Definitely...
...Huh? That's—Damn it!!
Mwahahaha!
*Shriek*
A demon?!
B-Blood?! Why?!
*Scream*
>A sudden rush of demons start to attack the adults.
Rika, Newbie!
Already on it! Devil Download!!
I'll take this group!
Thanks! Shit! What the hell is goin' on!?!
Huh?! Why isn't Mommy getting up?
Mommy!! Daddy!! I'm scared!
Waaaaaaaaah!
Everyone! Get behind me!!
Oh...? These ones will make perfect sacrifices for Lord Moloch.
Wait. You there, little girl...you aren't human, are you?
This scent... A homunculus? Such trash cannot be a sacrifice.
It's only value is being dead!
...!! Devil Download!!
Damn it! More are jumpin' in!
This is terrible! The demons are infiltrating our world!!
What?! Stop now, Moloch!!
Bastard, what're you thinkin'?!
Hmm? I told you, didn't I? I'm giving humanity purpose.
Your world will also fall in time. I'm just reaping the harvest
and building up my own power beforehand!
Building up your power?
There are still demons here foolish enough to challenge me.
Sacrificial meals help my subordinates and I eliminate them.
So, you've been slaughterin' humanity for your own benefit...?!
However, this world was too small to satisfy me.
I've eaten up all in this world, but it's still not enough.
I soon realized that if this world lacks humans—
I should eat those in other worlds, too!
More sacrifices equals more power! I'll break down every wall
and devour every human in existence!
Such behavior will interfere with the law of the universe!
If the laws of physics mix with the space-time continuum,
those jumbled worlds will disappear entirely!
I highly doubt that.
Nevertheless, we can't just let you be!
Megakin, Vince! Let's take him down!!
Hold it, WiFi Girl. I've got one more question for Moloch.
Oh? Go on. I'm in a charitable mood.
I'll answer anything if you ask now.
That leg lyin' over there. Did you eat the rest of it?
>Vince points to a leg. The shoe matches the one on the roof.
>There is no body.
Ah, that!
Yes, it was delectable. Child sacrifices are my favorite.
It was wandering around the hole, so I gobbled it up.
Baby flesh is delicious. It's best cooked alive.
And those dying screams for its mother are simply irresistible!
You bastard...!
...I get it, demon fucker.
Oh?
I love Irish stew.
The aged mutton flavor goes perfect with red wine.
That's why I'll fuck up anyone so stupid...
as to try lamb instead!
C'mon, boss man! Let's turn this guy into mince meat!
...Right!
Fools! We are not the same!
